The paper discusses the utilization of measure concentration phenomena in machine learning, which is a topic primarily studied in the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions the use of linear functionals and classifiers, which are topics studied in cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.ST (Statistics). The paper also discusses the construction of non-iterative procedures, which is a topic studied in cs.MS (Mathematical Software) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
